OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778746039
OL,3,CAll new Guernsey buildings must have
OL,4,Csolar panels or other renewables
OL,6,FGuernsey developers must include solar
OL,7,Fpanels or other renewable technology
OL,8,Fin all new buildings.
OL,10,FThe decision by the island's
OL,11,FDevelopment and Planning Authority
OL,12,F(DPA) follows a commitment by the
OL,13,FStates in 2023 to increase the amount
OL,14,Fof electricity generated locally,
OL,15,Freducing the reliance on imported
OL,16,Fenergy.
OL,18,FThe Island Development Plan also sets
OL,19,Fout an expectation to harness power
OL,20,Ffrom renewable sources.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778746039
OL,3,CAll new Guernsey buildings must have
OL,4,Csolar panels or other renewables
OL,6,FIf an appropriate amount of roof-
OL,7,Fmounted solar panels is not possible,
OL,8,Fplanners will consider other solar
OL,9,Fproducts, heat pumps and battery
OL,10,Fstorage to bridge the gap with
OL,11,Fapplications assessed on a case-by-
OL,12,Fcase basis.
OL,14,FDeputy Neil Inder, President of the
OL,15,FDPA, explains: "Making solar panels
OL,16,Fmandatory on new developments is good
OL,17,Ffor our environment and is good for
OL,18,Four energy security, all in line with
OL,19,Fthe States-approved Electricity
OL,20,FStrategy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1778746039
OL,3,CAll new Guernsey buildings must have
OL,4,Csolar panels or other renewables
OL,6,F"It's good that some developers
OL,7,Falready do this as standard, but
OL,8,Fmaking it mandatory means that we're
OL,9,Fmaking the most of the opportunities
OL,10,Fthat new developments pose.
OL,12,F"It's also cheaper to install these
OL,13,Fduring the build rather than fitting
OL,14,Fthem somewhere down the line."
OL,16,FDeputy Adrian Gabriel, President of
OL,17,Fthe Environment and Infrastructure
OL,18,FCommittee, adds: "Making this the norm
OL,19,Fwill undoubtedly help Guernsey in
OL,20,Fachieving its renewable energy
OL,21,Ftargets."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
